        "Description": "You were always the best. Nobody ever came close. Even after ten years, you define the art, and it defines you. If there&apos;s one thing I&apos;ve learned over the past decade, it&apos;s that no one is untouchable.\r\rThat brings me to today&apos;s assignment. It should be simple for someone as experienced as you, 47. It may even make you feel a tad nostalgic.\r\rI will leave you to prepare.\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as lukefsje.",
